    <div class="main review-item" id="5454028">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5454028/" class="title-link">寻求中国特色的民主</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5454028"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/tree0824/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2235850-54.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/tree0824/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">小树先生</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-06-04"
      class="main-meta">2012-06-04 21:57:36</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5454028_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  在中国近代政治思想史上，民主可能是出现频率最高的核心词汇。在晚清亡国灭种的危机下，觉醒的士大夫发现西方富强的重要原因是“君臣一体”，遂对民主制度产生向往。经晚清到五四两代知识分子的引介和阐释，民主这一价值几乎获得了绝对的正当性，以致有研究者形容，即使连最专...

